{"tid":142980,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"那年六四 遍地野屍 月下誰能逃","createTime":"2017-03-04T08:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T08:05:02.000Z","uid":49157,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8fdd61ae79b62a5a309b42d2d6a228c8b4f7255d","tid":142980,"uid":49157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T08:56:08.000Z","msg":"那年六四  遍地野屍<br />\n月下誰能逃<br />\n再殘酷再無力眼淚再多<br />\n坦克照碌過<br />\n無數生靈狂暴軍隊一律掃清<br />\n根本侮辱了生命<br />\n強權下愈寧靜愈變得不受壓抑<br />\n共產  最終出意外<br />\n六六年大飢荒  沒糧食供應餓死無命賠<br />\n別再靠中央  睡夢中醒覺<br />\n掰大眼看看這朽壞政府<br />\n答應過未能干預  只好單單案釋法<br />\n說自由說為民虛偽  只想要壓榨<br />\n無懼發動文革  引發大型災難<br />\n乜水都拉去批鬥<br />\n殺萬民卻為權力嗎  可會悔疚<br />\n這黑暗未來  後悔嗎  問問毛澤東<br />\n有冇高手可以幫手諗埋後面既verse/chorus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好冇粗口"},{"pid":"d3196eff4bbb249ea882c5b4d9f0045a26f6aaaa","tid":142980,"uid":49157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d5b1cec07299a4cc89cb947491a167de728dbd61","tid":142980,"uid":49157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:22:44.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"177bc509cbe605ee6d35d13a7cc3dc973ee48213","tid":142980,"uid":49157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d433a23d4cc9e6d62b1fa4ac06305452b548f8","tid":142980,"uid":86578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:29:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"43247c43c963f2fd650960dd30a1312db35bf59a","tid":142980,"uid":39295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc071a662fb5e00becba5c2425b297fcfaad41eb","tid":142980,"uid":15323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:36:42.000Z","msg"